itsy-bitsy-bash-script-repo
===========================

This collection of small used scripts is mainly commited to prevent them for getting lost in space and maybe someone out there could use a itsy-bitsy piece of code.

* Example usage
---------------

*/5 */8 * * * /home/ctietze/cronscripts/diskalert.sh >> /home/ctietze/cronlogs/diskalert.log

